# Trivy vulnerability suppressions (CVE / vuln IDs only).
#
# Policy:
# - One ID per line; optional end-of-line comment with rationale + review/expiry date.
# - Do not use wildcards or disable entire scanners here — that hides real issues.
# - Record the same rationale in docs/TESTING.md or the PR so reviewers can audit.
#
# Example (remove leading # when adding a real reviewed suppression):
# CVE-2024-12345678  # reason: not applicable / fixed in next base image bump; review-by 2026-06-01
